    <ol start="1" type="1">
        <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify"><span lang="EN-IN" 
                style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">Payments by Members shall be made with 
            his/her credit card or debit card. The Member is under obligation to ensure that 
            the account from which the amounts are to be collected have sufficient funds or 
            credit available to cover any charges. Member is solely responsible for any 
            associated bank or credit card charges or fees. Member may be charged a 
            processing fee for a declined credit or debit card payment.</span></li>
        <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify"><span lang="EN-IN" 
                style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">In the event the Member defaults on any 
            payments, Vroom is entitled to charge reminder fees and default interest in 
            accordance with the provisions of the law. In addition, Vroom may utilize third 
            parties to collect amounts owed to Vroom by a Member.</span></li>
        <li class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify"><span lang="EN-IN" 
                style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">With all fees mentioned above, Vroom 
            reserves the right to prohibit a Member from making a subsequent reservation 
            until all outstanding fees in the Member&#39;s account have been paid in full. In 
            the event a fee is incurred, Members will receive an email invoice from Vroom 
            that will have detailed payment instructions.</span></li>
    </ol>
